              "value": "Rewrite sentence (b) so that it means the same as sentence (a).\n1. a. Governments should interfere to ban bad practices in schools.\n   b. It’s high time ........................................................\n2. a. If strict measures are not taken, the educational system will deteriorate.\n   b. Unless .................................................................\n3. a. I have a strong desire that all governments will ban cigarettes production.\n   b. I wish .................................................................."
